      "title": "Executive Summary",
      "content": {
        "summary": "The university's July 2026 financial report shows significant overspending in Facilities and Services categories across all departments, with variance totals exceeding $30,000. Payroll expenses are within budget, but student collection rates missed targets, indicating potential revenue shortfalls. The Facilities category shows the largest variances, particularly in Health Sciences and Arts & Humanities departments.",
